<item>
            <title>[LU-7584] sanity test_129: current dir size 24576, previous limit 24576</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7584</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Saurabh Tandan &amp;lt;saurabh.tandan@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/3eac1b80-a26d-11e5-bdef-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/3eac1b80-a26d-11e5-bdef-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_129 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;CMD: shadow-53vm3 test -e /sys/fs/ldiskfs/dm-3/max_dir_size
CMD: shadow-53vm3 echo 0 &amp;gt;/sys/fs/ldiskfs/dm-3/max_dir_size
return code 28 received as expected
current dir size 24576, previous limit 24576
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Appears to be similar to &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2479&quot; title=&quot;sanity.sh test_129: max dir size limit work incorrectly.&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-2479&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-2479&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>EL7.1 Server/EL7.1 Client - DNE&lt;br/&gt;
Master, build# 3270</environment>
